        "text": "(a) So what did Chizkiyah actually do?\n(b) He erred however, in a ruling of Shmuel.   What did Shmuel say about announcing Nisan on the thirtieth of Adar?\n(c) Why is that?\n(d) What was the basis of Chizkiyah's mistake?"
      },
      {
        "id": "q17",
