        "id": "q22",
        "label": "22)",
        "text": "(a) What does Rebbi Yossi b'Rebbi Chanina citing Rebbi Eliezer ben Ya'akov comment, based on the word \"Tamid\" in the Pasuk there \"Over aleini Tamid \"?\n(b) What does he also say based on the Pasuk in Tehilim \"mi'Ma'amakim Kerasicha Hash-m\"?\n(c) What does the Beraisa add to that based on the same Pasuk plus the Pasuk there \"Tefilah le'Ani ki Ya'atof\"?"
      },
      {
        "id": "q23",
