        "text": "(a) What did Mar Zutra throw in front of Rav Ashi when together with Ameimar, they were once eating together?\n(b) What did he answer when Rav Ashi queried him from the Beraisa which forbids throwing food?\n(c) And what did he retort when Rav Ashi queried him from another Beraisa which equates other food with bread?\n(d) How did he reconcile the two Beraisos (and justify his action)?\n(e) What is an example of food that gets spoilt when one throws it?"
      },
      {
        "id": "q19",
        "label": "19)",
