    "questions": [
      {
        "id": "q1",
        "label": "1)",
        "text": "(a) What does the Nun in 'Huna' indicate when seen in a dream?\n(b) What distinction does the Tana now draw between 'Huna' and 'Chanina', 'Chananya' and 'Yochanan'?\n(c) What is the basis of the latter interpretation?\n(d) On what basis does seeing 'Hesped' in a dream signify that Hash-m has had pity on the dreamer and will redeem him from troubles?\n(e) What condition does the Tana give with regard to all the interpretations mentioned in this question?"
      },
