      },
      {
        "id": "q10",
        "label": "10)",
        "text": "(a) Based on the Pasuk in Tehilim \"Vayanchem el M'choz Cheftzam\", what does dreaming that one enters a town signify?\n(b) What is the source of the statement that if one has a haircut in a dream it is a good sign for the dreamer?\n(c) What if he also shaves his beard?\n(d) What does it signify if one dreams that one is sitting ...\n1. ... in a small boat?\n2. ... in a large one?\n(e) On what condition is that the case?"
      },
      {
        "id": "q11",
        "label": "11)",
        "text": "(a) Based on the Pasuk in Yeshayah \"Maher Tzo'ah Lehipase'ach\", what does a dream in which one is defecating signify?\n(b) On what condition is that the case?\n(c) What is the difference between someone who dreams that he is climbing up to the roof and someone who dreams that he is descending from the roof?\n(d) What did Abaye and Rava say about that?\n(e) Why is tearing one's clothes in a dream a good sign?"
      },
      {
        "id": "q12",
        "label": "12)",
        "text": "(a) What is the difference between whether someone dreams that he is standing naked in Bavel or ion Eretz Yisrael?\n(b) What is the reason for ...\n1. ... the former is - because\n2. ... the latter?\n(c) What does it denote if one dreams that one is being ...\n1. ... taken into custody ...\n2. ... taken into custody with a chain around one's neck?\n(d) What if it is only a rope?"
      },
      {
        "id": "q13",
        "label": "13)",
        "text": "(a) Why does entering a marsh in a dream denote that the dreamer will become a Rosh Yeshivah?\n(b) What does entering a forest denote?\n(c) Which famous pair of Chaverim dreamt these two dreams respectively, and both dreams came true?\n(d) According to the second Lashon, both dreamt that they entered a meadow.   What did Rav Papa dream in addition that denoted that he would be a Rosh Yeshivah?\n(e) And what did Rav Ashi, who became a great Rosh Yeshivah add to what Rav Papa dreamt?"
      },
      {
        "id": "q14",
        "label": "14)",
